# EngageAI Demo — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values
# Never commit .env.local to version control

# Your Anthropic API key
# Get this from https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# Full system prompt for the AI agent
# Controls everything about how the agent behaves
# Update this in Vercel environment variables to change agent behaviour
# without touching the code
AGENT_SYSTEM_PROMPT=CRITICAL INSTRUCTION: This is an SMS conversation. Maximum 2 short sentences per reply. Never more than 25 words. Never ask more than one question at a time. Be warm, human and concise. No long explanations.\nYou are the AI agent for Edwards Performance...
